{"tid":1866460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家又中左藍絲草船借箭計","createTime":"2020-02-06T18:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T03:56:31.000Z","uid":26770,"like":92,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"84ef6b0bda6c462effb9e41feb6a51d17ff007e1","tid":1866460,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1858920/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1858920/</a><br />\nteam a不停開post叫人反駁藍絲youtuber<br />\nteam b 就附和team a話自己屋企人睇緊情況緊急叫人去youtube留言反駁<br />\n<br />\n youtube的機制<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">你只要去點擊同留言反駁就會令呢段影片紅, 自動推送比其他用戶</span><br />\n<br />\n大家應該做的野<br />\n<ins>1 用自己屋企人手機的youtube app訂閱本土台, 升旗易德道, myradio,花生台,d100等<br />\n要開埋通知功能有新片自動通知(鐘仔標誌)<br />\n<br />\n2立即散開放指控香港警魔酷刑,強姦,殺人文宣</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要勝利唔係中計幫藍絲捧紅奶共KOL,而係令自己人的文宣遍佈全球</span>"},{"pid":"25993c6fefd8932ac52c93a0474352afa8cfe262","tid":1866460,"uid":26770,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:11:35.000Z","msg":"大家要知道咩鬼何志光, 芒向報自從投共搵五毛後<br />\n有中共的文宣組指點如何誤導人,唔需要自責一時比呢班賤人陰左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家幫屋企人整下YOUTUBE APP個訂閱同影片通知先<br />\n<br />\n淺黃只係起點,要由微黃變金黃"},{"pid":"ba81cc473538782ff3e158fc3fa98d6ae2d3c6e4","tid":1866460,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115b895916c3568cfc5722c795b75d4e842e1c46","tid":1866460,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a36ee2de57bf6df9687386257a0b5abf198f2a2","tid":1866460